      "description": "Constraint is limited to non-cannulated titanium-alloy pedicle screws with nominal outer diameter 7.5 mm and thread pitch 2.75 mm, tested under monotonic quasi-static compression-bending per ASTM F1717 Section 8. Cannulated variants, dynamic fatigue loading, and screws outside the 6.5–8.5 mm diameter range are explicitly excluded from this COU."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
