      "name": "ASTM F1717 quasi-static compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Displacement-controlled crosshead rate 25 ± 2.5 mm/min; test block separation 44.45 mm (ASTM F1717 nominal); ambient temperature 23 ± 2 °C; construct axial pre-load 0 N (pure bending mode). FEA mesh element size 0.15–0.40 mm in screw-rod interface region; Ti-6Al-4V material properties: E = 114 ± 3 GPa, σ_y = 880 ± 20 MPa. All QoIs (stiffness, yield force, F@40 mm) evaluated within 0–40 mm crosshead displacement range."
    }
